{"tid":264658,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點儲三百萬首期(六百萬以上樓)？","createTime":"2017-05-31T04:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T04:15:34.000Z","uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a86c99a11e14b22cc430a5cf00f831ed5be0bfcf","tid":264658,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"好多市區樓已經超過六百萬，意味無得再按八成，得返六成按揭。首期最低消費已經係二百四十萬以上，仲要印花稅，律師費等等。準備三百萬已經係上車預算。<br />\n<br />\n有無三十歲左右的人分享點儲到首期？畢業起計每年儲蓄幾多，投資複合增長幾多？我而家諗法係收入持續增長的話應該仲有機會的。"},{"pid":"29f1601604a74b1a93741731e29b6f6d25aa6263","tid":264658,"uid":18555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:09:48.000Z","msg":"所以個個就去買新樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b23a09dc8bcf8f46c3994850db5c29f4871cb53","tid":264658,"uid":70685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:13:13.000Z","msg":"冇可能啦 除非有父幹"},{"pid":"3fa97f791bcd318a0612a00aa8fe36a68b1958f6","tid":264658,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以個個就去買新樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新樓係八成五按？但好多都成八百萬九百萬，發展商按揭點計利息？"},{"pid":"daa1e6013192f0f8a46de85002ee4af09d798dbb","tid":264658,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:15:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}